cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. 

This paper focuses on developing models for engaging dialogue grounded in images, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper uses state-of-the-art image and text representations and designs natural architectures, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper also evaluates the efficacy of the approach using automatic metrics and human evaluations, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR).
